  "text": "Tafiei-Naeini and McCann [CITATION_1] suggested better resolution with multiple current sources at the expense of EIT hardware. Their proposed system was not only complex but also required balanced output impedance and phase among the current sources. The SNR of the excitation current source also added to the spatial resolution of the EIT systems. A current sub-system was designed to provide an SNR of 80 dB.",
